WEBVTT

00:00.353 --> 00:02.469
- Previously on Underground...
- What's your business here?

00:02.521 --> 00:04.806
We could work together,
apprehend these runaways

00:04.807 --> 00:05.807
and split the bounty.

00:05.809 --> 00:06.939
Want to be a moral leader?

00:06.977 --> 00:09.227
The begins at home.

00:09.278 --> 00:11.637
Now I promised that I was gonna
get you back in that shop.

00:11.698 --> 00:13.198
I need you working on the grandstand

00:13.199 --> 00:14.198
for my nomination announcement.

00:14.954 --> 00:15.916
I saw him, Daddy.

00:15.952 --> 00:17.618
Sam... I saw him running.

00:17.670 --> 00:18.843
We don't know where we running to.

00:18.894 --> 00:20.371
"Wolf," "underworld," "angel"?

00:20.373 --> 00:22.173
Don't none of that
sound like freedom to me.

00:22.208 --> 00:23.341
It sound like death.

00:24.844 --> 00:26.094
Henry!

00:31.285 --> 00:34.585
Stay with us, Noah.

00:37.271 --> 00:38.247
They're still coming for us.

00:38.283 --> 00:40.670
The Undertaker's gonna take us
to the next station.

00:43.159 --> 00:44.359
Put him here!

00:45.746 --> 00:47.445
He lost too much blood!

00:47.448 --> 00:48.447
What happened?

00:48.499 --> 00:49.448
We got to get this bullet out!

00:49.450 --> 00:50.448
Ain't no time.

00:50.451 --> 00:51.500
Fire got some, but not all.

00:51.534 --> 00:53.368
- Got who?
- Patty Cannon Gang.

00:53.420 --> 00:54.786
- I need a knife.
- We need to move him now!

00:54.838 --> 00:56.537
Hey, I can't risk taking
him to the next station,

00:56.590 --> 00:58.039
compromising the whole cell.

00:58.091 --> 01:00.792
Just give us a wagon!
We give ourself a head start.

01:00.793 --> 01:02.210
They gonna spot you before
you get to the river.

01:02.262 --> 01:05.063
Look, these bodies are bound
to go to the graveyard

01:05.066 --> 01:06.242
in PappyJack.

01:06.278 --> 01:07.551
We'll hide you in there.

01:07.585 --> 01:08.679
Won't get you across the river,

01:08.680 --> 01:11.552
but it'll get you a good head start.

01:11.605 --> 01:12.688
Henry...

01:15.058 --> 01:18.609
All right, we gonna put
this devil's snare in here.

01:18.644 --> 01:20.144
It gonna help with the swelling.

01:20.146 --> 01:21.313
Move, house girl!

01:21.364 --> 01:22.813
There ain't no time
to be standing around!

01:22.865 --> 01:24.483
They gonna be here any minute!

01:24.534 --> 01:27.152
I thought the crosses signaled for four.

01:30.990 --> 01:32.323
One of us didn't make it.

01:33.877 --> 01:35.043
Legs!

01:36.914 --> 01:38.629
Listen carefully now.
Be careful with him!

01:38.664 --> 01:39.831
When you reach the river,
head west for two miles

01:39.883 --> 01:42.167
to a rickety bridge
that looks like a crooked smile.

01:42.218 --> 01:44.002
Listen, when you cross it,
go to the top of the hill,

01:44.054 --> 01:46.638
look for a house
got a lantern in the window.

01:46.673 --> 01:48.890
Belongs to a man
named John, John Hawkes.

01:48.926 --> 01:52.377
Tell him a friend of a friend sent you.

